<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="run-away-from">run away (from)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>逃走；逃避：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The thief heard the noise and ran away quickly. 
小偷听到声音，匆忙逃走了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s irresponsible of you to run away from difficulties.
见了困难就躲是不负责的。</p></div></div>